                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7231" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1132</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8185 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国易物流：从双轮驱动到商业生态的成长之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Guoyi Logistics: The growth road from two-wheel drive to business ecology</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王东升，王一冰，王美嘉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山西国易物流有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会识别；双轮驱动；规模经济；范围经济；平台化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Opportunity identification;  Double wheel drive; Economy of scale;  Economy of scope; Platformization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">扩张欲望是企业最本质的欲望之一。作为实现扩张的主要方式，追求成长
成为企业的使命。本案例通过描述国易物流从“创立钢材贸易和仓储业务——扩
张道路中规模经济与范围经济选择——平台化转型”的成长历程，引导学员重点
关注企业从创建到成长的四个关键问题：一是创建企业的机会识别、发现和利用，
二是企业内部协同效应对企业效率提升和成本降低的途径，三是企业扩张路径应
该如何选择：规模经济、范围经济抑或其他？四是企业如何实现平台化成长。
本案例在一定程度上回应了海尔集团张瑞敏所论述的“企业平台化”趋势，
对于在成熟市场中追求成长的企业具有借鉴和启示意义。

</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The desire to expand is one of the most essential desires of enterprises. 
This case describes the growth process of Guoyi Logistics from &quot;establishing steel trade 
and warehousing business -- choice of scale economy and scope economy in expansion 
road -- platform transformation&quot;, and guides students to focus on the four key issues 
from creation to growth: The first is the identification, discovery and utilization of 
opportunities to establish enterprises; the second is the way that the internal synergies 
can improve the efficiency and reduce the cost of enterprises; the third is how to choose 
the expansion path of enterprises: economies of scale, economies of scope or others. 
Fourth, how enterprises achieve platform growth. 
This case responds to the trend of &quot;enterprise platformization&quot; discussed by Zhang 
Ruimin of Haier Group to a certain extent, and has reference significance for enterprises 
pursuing growth in mature markets.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《工商管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机会发现理论；企业行为过程；协同效应；马太效应；亚马逊分轮；规模经济与范围经济；安索夫矩阵；平台战略理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
